<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .alert {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>New Login to Your Account</h2>
        
        <div class="alert">
            <p>We detected a new login to your account from an unfamiliar location.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="details">
            <h3>Login Details:</h3>
            <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{ Timestamp | date: "%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p UTC" }}</p>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{ Location }}</p>
            <p><strong>IP Address:</strong> {{ IpAddress }}</p>
            <p><strong>Device:</strong> {{ DeviceInfo }}</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>If this was you, you can ignore this email. If you don't recognize this activity, please:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Change your password immediately</li>
            <li>Enable two-factor authentication if not already enabled</li>
            <li>Contact our support team at {{ SupportEmail }}</li>
        </ol>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated security alert. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p>&copy; {{ "now" | date: "%Y" }} Local Services Marketplace. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
